OL,3,CFormer MP and current Senedd Member
OL,4,Cappear in court accused of betting
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FFormer Conservative Member of
OL,8,FParliament Craig Williams, along with
OL,9,Fother senior Conservatives, have
OL,10,Fappeared in court accused of cheating
OL,11,Fby gambling on the date of the 2024
OL,12,Fgeneral election.
OL,14,FCraig Williams, 39, who served as the
OL,15,FTory MP for Montgomeryshire and
OL,16,FCardiff North, has been charged with
OL,17,Fcheating at gambling and three counts
OL,18,Fof enabling or assisting others to
OL,19,Fcheat.
