OL,7,FWilliams served as parliamentary
OL,8,Fprivate secretary to Rishi Sunak
OL,9,Fduring his time as prime minister.
OL,11,FAt Westminster Magistrates Court on
OL,12,FFriday, Williams appeared alongside 14
OL,13,Fothers charged with similar offences.
OL,15,FOthers included member of Senedd
OL,16,FRussell George, 50, and Thomas James,
OL,17,F38, the suspended director of the
OL,18,FWelsh Conservatives, both of whom
OL,19,Findicated not guilty pleas.
