OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThe charges come after "Operation
OL,8,FScott" was launched to investigate
OL,9,Fgambling by politicians and employees
OL,10,Fof the Conservative Party in the lead-
OL,11,Fup to the 2024 general election.
OL,13,FRishi Sunak, who has provided a
OL,14,Fwitness statement in this case, had
OL,15,Fnoted that elections would take place
OL,16,Fin the second half of the year but had
OL,17,Fnot given a date.
