OL,4,Cappear in court accused of betting
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FProsecuting on behalf of the Gambling
OL,8,FCommission, Sam Stein KC said:
OL,9,F"Operation Scott was an investigation
OL,10,Flaunched by the gambling commission
OL,11,Finto politicians and employees of the
OL,12,FConservative Party, and a former
OL,13,Fpolice officer ... who had placed bets
OL,14,Fon the date of the 2024 general
OL,15,Felection with the benefit of
OL,16,Fconfidential or insider information as
OL,17,Fto when that date might be.
OL,19,F"The prosecution says that placing
OL,20,Fbets with inside information is a
OL,21,Fcriminal offence, namely cheating."
