OL,7,FWilliams was first the MP for Cardiff
OL,8,FNorth between 2015 and 2017 before he
OL,9,Flost his seat to Labour MP Anna
OL,10,FMcMorrin.
OL,12,FHe was then elected as the MP for
OL,13,FMontgomeryshire at the 2019 general
OL,14,Felection which he lost in July last
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FBefore the July 4 election was called,
OL,18,Fplanning took place at Downing Street
OL,19,Fand Conservative Campaign
OL,20,FHeadquarters, the court heard.
