OL,7,FThe 15 defendants are alleged to have
OL,8,Fplaced bets based on confidential
OL,9,Finformation gained from those rooms,
OL,10,For enabling others to place bets by
OL,11,Fpassing that information on.
OL,13,FIf convicted they could face up to two
OL,14,Fyears in prison for these offences.
OL,16,FTwelve of the defendants indicated not
OL,17,Fguilty pleas.
